<h1>Queue jobs now</h1>

<p>Click on any of the links below to enqueue that job from within this web
request. Native Que jobs record an <code>enqueue.que</code> event (or a single
<code>bulk_enqueue.que</code> event for a bulk enqueue); Active Job jobs (and
mailers) record an <code>enqueue.active_job</code> event.</p>

<ul>
  <% @worker_tests.each do |(type, worker, test)| %>
    <% label = "#{type}: #{worker}#{" - #{test}" unless test == :default}" %>
    <li><%= link_to label, queue_workers_path(:type => type, :worker => worker, :test => test) %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>
